  <!-- EN: Credit bond -->
  <USAC_AssaultRig.label>軌道突擊鑽機</USAC_AssaultRig.label>
  <!-- EN: Armed groups produce and deploy these flexibly deployable drilling rigs to the surface via on-orbit industrial platforms to carry out mining operations. Their mining methods cause severe surface pollution, which you can prevent by destroying them to contain the pollution and avoid deposit loss.\n\nAlternatively, you can allow them to leave on their own after mining is complete. Regardless, armed groups will deploy troops and supplies to protect their property from intrusion. -->
  <USAC_AssaultRig.helpText>武裝集團透過在軌工業平台生產與投放這種能夠靈活部署的鑽機平台到地面上執行開採任務，所使用的開採方式會對地表造成嚴重的污染，你能夠將其摧毀來遏制污染的發生並避免礦藏的損失。也可以放任其開採完畢後自行離開。無論如何，武裝集團都會派駐部隊與物資來保護他們的財產不受他人侵犯。</USAC_AssaultRig.helpText>
  
  <!-- EN: Bodybag -->
  <USAC_Bodybag.label>裹屍袋</USAC_Bodybag.label>
  <!-- EN: Bodybag is a designated packaging container for medical departments to package organic materials in transactions. USAC have a long history of legally acquiring such unclaimed materials for peaceful research, biological experiments, and medical aesthetics.\n\nBodybag containing samples must be placed within trade beacon range. Furthermore, materials with drug resistance can provide additional market value.\n\nIt is important to note that body bags cannot prevent environmental microorganisms from damaging the integrity of the materials; therefore, for large-scale long-term preservation, large cold storage facilities should be considered to prevent the loss of value due to natural decay. -->
  <USAC_Bodybag.helpText>裹屍袋是武裝集團醫療部門用於在交易中包裹材料的指定包裝物。武裝集團長期收購這些無人認領的屍體用於和平研究、生物實驗與醫療美容。在交易中需要將裝有樣本的裹屍袋放置於交易信標的範圍內，此外具有藥物耐受性的材料可提供額外的販售價值。\n\n要注意裹屍袋無法阻止環境微生物對材料完整性的損壞，因此在大規模的長期保存時應考慮構築大型冷庫以防止材料自然腐壞對價值的損失。</USAC_Bodybag.helpText>
  
  <!-- EN: Credit bonds -->
  <USAC_CreditBonds.label>信用債券</USAC_CreditBonds.label>
  <!-- EN: Armed groups and related traders used a form of value called credit bonds as a substitute for silver in the trade. These bonds could only be obtained through specific material transactions, and their registered nature made them difficult to circulate through other means. -->
  <USAC_CreditBonds.helpText>武裝集團與相關貿易商在軍火貿易中使用一種名為信用債券的價值抵用物作為白銀的替代，這些債券只能夠透過特定的物資交易來獲取，並且其記名性使得債券無法透過其他的方式流通。</USAC_CreditBonds.helpText>
  
